<br>
this apology is forwarded to Spehres of Honor, so if anyone knows their website, please forward this to them.  I am sorry if this causes hardship for anyone in the VH.  Obviously, this situation was not intentional, and we left the area as soon as we were informed that their raid had indeed not been cancelled.<br>
